title: Padre Island National Seashore: Amphibians
body: Explore This Park    Learn About the Park     Nature     Animals     Amphibians                Amphibians         Woodhouse's toad in the sand dunes at Padre Island National Seashore. NPS photo  The following frogs and toads have been documented within Padre Island National Seashore. Please note this list may not be all-inclusive. Frogs Rio Grande Leopard Frog - Rana Berlandieri Green Treefrog - Hyla cinerea Spotted Chorus Frog - Pseudacris clarkii   Toads  Hurter's Spadefoot - Scaphiopus hurterii Woodhouse's Toad- Bufo w. woodhousii GulfCoast Toad - Bufo valliceps Texas Toad - Bufo speciosus Great Plains Narrowmouth Toad- Gastrophryne Olivacea Couch's Spadefoot - Scaphiopus couchii
